  "short_description": "Pixel Fireplace is a cozy, type-controlled simulation. Type commands to strike a match, throw logs onto the crackling fire and watch them burn down to hot coals in real-time. Discover commands with the hint system, or just sit back, turn the lights down and enjoy.",
