  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678480/extras/6ae2a74b1944e3392ccbe2b325621165.poster.avif?t=1770573273\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678480/extras/6ae2a74b1944e3392ccbe2b325621165.webm?t=1770573273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678480/extras/6ae2a74b1944e3392ccbe2b325621165.mp4?t=1770573273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pixel Fireplace is a cozy, type-controlled simulation. Type commands to strike a match, throw logs onto the crackling fire and watch them burn down to hot coals in real-time (about 25 min per log). Discover commands with the hint system, or just sit back, turn the lights down and enjoy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678480/extras/fc45ae5f64ba79d2213010a5559b6547.avif?t=1770573273\" width=532 height=162 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hint System</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Letters appear gold if they're part of a command word.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678480/extras/381ea62264ef7bb2eb1496caa9af39d7.poster.avif?t=1770573273\" width=414 height=34 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678480/extras/381ea62264ef7bb2eb1496caa9af39d7.webm?t=1770573273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678480/extras/381ea62264ef7bb2eb1496caa9af39d7.mp4?t=1770573273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Second Monitor Support</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run Pixel Fireplace on a second monitor while you work. Double-click to switch to windowed mode, then drag the window to another screen and double-click again for fullscreen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678480/extras/3a243baaed5b5b1db19126494ed4e0bf.avif?t=1770573273\" width=556 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a cozy work atmosphere :) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to Play</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1) Type the word <i>FIREPLACE</i> on the title screen to begin.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678480/extras/5e8fde147df1c73b9fdcfbf6ef2fbb33.poster.avif?t=1770573273\" width=378 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678480/extras/5e8fde147df1c73b9fdcfbf6ef2fbb33.webm?t=1770573273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678480/extras/5e8fde147df1c73b9fdcfbf6ef2fbb33.mp4?t=1770573273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2) Follow the prompts by typing <i>LOG</i> and then <i>MATCH</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3) Use the hint system described above to discover more commands. Here are a few to get started! <i>MARSHMALLOW</i>, <i>SMORE</i>, <i>HOTDOG</i>, <i>FIRECRACKER</i>, <i>NEWSPAPER</i>, <i>BLUE</i>, <i>SUNSET</i>, <i>WATER</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to Quit</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1) Press the Esc key or type <i>WATER</i> to exit from the fireplace screen to the title screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2) Press the Esc key at the title screen to quit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678480/extras/d660a3b9909e090d15f75c03799a6fe0.poster.avif?t=1770573273\" width=266 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678480/extras/d660a3b9909e090d15f75c03799a6fe0.webm?t=1770573273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678480/extras/6ae2a74b1944e3392ccbe2b325621165.poster.avif?t=1770573273\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678480/extras/6ae2a74b1944e3392ccbe2b325621165.webm?t=1770573273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678480/extras/6ae2a74b1944e3392ccbe2b325621165.mp4?t=1770573273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pixel Fireplace is a cozy, type-controlled simulation. Type commands to strike a match, throw logs onto the crackling fire and watch them burn down to hot coals in real-time (about 25 min per log). Discover commands with the hint system, or just sit back, turn the lights down and enjoy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678480/extras/fc45ae5f64ba79d2213010a5559b6547.avif?t=1770573273\" width=532 height=162 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hint System</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Letters appear gold if they're part of a command word.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678480/extras/381ea62264ef7bb2eb1496caa9af39d7.poster.avif?t=1770573273\" width=414 height=34 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678480/extras/381ea62264ef7bb2eb1496caa9af39d7.webm?t=1770573273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678480/extras/381ea62264ef7bb