ress the Esc key or type <i>WATER</i> to exit from the fireplace screen to the title screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2) Press the Esc key at the title screen to quit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678480/extras/d660a3b9909e090d15f75c03799a6fe0.poster.avif?t=1770573273\" width=266 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2678480/extras/d660a3b9909e090d15f75c03799a6fe0.webm?t=1770573273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
